## Tipos de Dados

```typescript
type Priority = 'alta' | 'media' | 'baixa'

interface Member {
  id: string
  name: string
  role: string
  avatar: string        // iniciais para avatar gerado via CSS
  color: string         // cor do avatar
  isOnline: boolean
}

interface ChecklistItem {
  id: string
  text: string
  done: boolean
}

interface Card {
  id: string
  title: string
  description: string
  priority: Priority
  assigneeId: string | null
  dueDate: string | null   // ISO date string
  checklist: ChecklistItem[]
  columnId: string
}

interface Column {
  id: string
  title: string
  cardIds: string[]
}

interface Board {
  id: string
  name: string
  columns: Column[]
}
```

---

## Estado Zustand (useFlowStore)

```typescript
interface FlowStore {
  // Dados
  boards: Board[]
  cards: Record<string, Card>   // mapa id → card
  members: Member[]

  // UI State
  activeBoardId: string
  selectedCardId: string | null
  searchQuery: string
  filterPriority: Priority | null
  filterMemberId: string | null
  darkMode: boolean

  // Actions
  addBoard(name: string): void
  addCard(columnId: string, title: string): void
  updateCard(id: string, updates: Partial<Card>): void
  deleteCard(id: string): void
  moveCard(cardId: string, fromCol: string, toCol: string, toIndex: number): void
  addChecklistItem(cardId: string, text: string): void
  toggleChecklistItem(cardId: string, itemId: string): void
  setActiveBoard(id: string): void
  setSearchQuery(q: string): void
  setFilterPriority(p: Priority | null): void
  setFilterMember(id: string | null): void
  toggleDarkMode(): void
}
```

Cards são armazenados em um mapa plano (`Record<string, Card>`). Colunas guardam apenas `cardIds[]`. Isso evita mutação aninhada e torna o reordenamento eficiente.

